<template>
    <a-auto-complete
        :dataSource="dataSource"
        style="width: 200px"
        @select="onSelect"
        @search="handleSearch"
        placeholder="input here"
    />
</template>
<script>
export default {
    data() {
        return {
            dataSource: []
        };
    },
    methods: {
        handleSearch(value) {
            this.dataSource = !value
                ? []
                : [value, value + value, value + value + value];
        },
        onSelect(value) {
            console.log("onSelect", value);
        }
    }
};
</script>
